8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 11=

11
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:43,159
By my decree:

12
00:00:43,759 --> 00:00:45,280
Princess Anhe, Mei Lin,

13
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:47,840
is betrothed to Prince Murong Xuanlie.

14
00:00:48,359 --> 00:00:50,399
General Muye Luomei

15
00:00:50,399 --> 00:00:52,719
is betrothed to Prince Murong Jinghe.

16
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:53,679
Father!

17
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:55,000
Are you defying my decree?

18
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,879
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Father.

19
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:19,079
Your Highness, I'm here.

20
00:01:23,159 --> 00:01:23,959
Your Highness?

21
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:33,079
You wish to marry Murong Xuanlie

22
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,879
and betray me?

23
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:37,640
Dream on!

24
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:42,879
Take her out of the capital.

25
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:45,400
This is the antidote
to the Lockjaw Drop.

26
00:01:45,519 --> 00:01:46,560
Have her take it.

27
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,719
When she wakes, tell her

28
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,239
once I've won,

29
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:51,280
I will come for her.

30
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,480
You've planned this for years.

31
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,439
At a time like this,

32
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:57,680
are you really going to
ruin it all for a woman?

33
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,439
This chessboard

34
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,359
is mine to play.

35
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:07,480
I don't need her
to sacrifice herself for it.

36
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:25,360
Beauty has long been blamed for chaos.

37
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:27,080
Quite the schemer

38
00:02:27,439 --> 00:02:29,639
to play His Highness like a puppet.

39
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:32,439
He'd wreck his own plans
just to save you.

40
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,919
Play?

41
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,879
Chaos?

42
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,000
Don't you

43
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,879
find your words ridiculous?

44
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,719
I'm just an orphan girl.

45
00:02:42,759 --> 00:02:44,680
If he hadn't fallen for me himself,

46
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,400
how could I have played

47
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,879
a prince so high above me?

48
00:02:48,639 --> 00:02:49,759
Such a clever tongue.

49
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,000
Whether it is clever speech or not,

50
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:55,120
you know best in your heart.

51
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:06,080
Mr. Pei.

52
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,319
You've known who I am all along.

53
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:10,080
Kill me or carve me up.

54
00:03:10,479 --> 00:03:11,520
Do as you wish.

55
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:13,719
Kill you?

56
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,280
With a face this fine,

57
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,840
killing you

58
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:20,199
would be a waste.

59
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:26,120
I plan to assassinate Murong Xuanlie

60
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,520
on the wedding day.

61
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:29,240
I want him dead!

62
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,719
So,

63
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,439
will you join me?

64
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:04,719
I went to such lengths to get you out,

65
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,240
yet you choose to throw it all away?

66
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:10,840
I know

67
00:04:11,039 --> 00:04:12,520
you did it for my sake.

68
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:15,599
But I don't like
leaving things unfinished.

69
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,680
The game isn't over yet.

70
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,720
Why throw away your blade?

71
00:04:40,279 --> 00:04:41,079
So...

72
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,759
You can't bear to lose me either.

73
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,639
Since that's the case,

74
00:04:53,079 --> 00:04:54,160
the throne and you,

75
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:56,079
I want them all.

76
00:05:19,980 --> 00:05:21,940
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

77
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:25,160
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

78
00:05:27,020 --> 00:05:28,500
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

79
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:32,180
ظآزLike blossoms that refuse to fadeظآز

80
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:35,980
ظآزIt asks no right or wrongظآز

81
00:05:36,220 --> 00:05:38,980
ظآزNor fears the turning of fateظآز

82
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:41,700
ظآزA trace of spring on the windظآز

83
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:44,340
ظآزA whisper of a broken heartظآز

84
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:48,300
ظآزA farewell song unfoldsظآز

85
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:51,500
ظآزCarrying every sorrow within itظآز

86
00:05:51,900 --> 00:05:53,940
ظآزKarma weaves its endless threadظآز

87
00:05:54,060 --> 00:05:57,900
ظآزAnd I would follow you
without turning backظآز

88
00:05:58,380 --> 00:06:01,380
ظآزLife and death become
nothing sharp or finalظآز

89
